{
  "text": "We will use the following results about the continuity of linear pseudodifferential operators with symbols in Gevrey-Hörmander classes, and we refer to [3, Theorem 2.1] and [CITATION_1] Theorem 3.7] respectively, for the proofs.",
  "correct_citation": {
